Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}高中生 南极…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:01:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么是烫的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为奶奶说 现在还是五月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算是五月 烫的东西还是烫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要冷饮 还有茶点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也想吃点布丁什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.06,0:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们不觉得我们这样很怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很怪？是你要我们做那种计划的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有脸嫌弃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是啊 妳知道我有多羞耻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也想不出别的方法了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那种事也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女高中生…去南极！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:36.17,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fn华康俪粗黑\bord0\fs25\1c&H474F4C&\pos(230,14)\frz340.6}「女高中生去南极！」现役女高中生歌星，将与民间观测队一道进行为期三个月的南极之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:39.40,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪粗黑\bord0\fs25\1c&H474F4C&\frz340.6\move(230,14,258,-144,0,3196)}「女高中生去南极！」现役女高中生歌星，将与民间观测队一道进行为期三个月的南极之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}预计今年出发的民间南极观测队日前宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一名现役女高中生将与拍摄组一同随队…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.07,0:02:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这名女高中生就是歌星白石结月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她的南极之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以及在昭和基地的生活将进行网络直播
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被抢先了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前那两个队员什么都没提
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是提了 这家伙会吵翻天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报导人员 记者 同行人员 我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石结月 她的事务所…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打电话到这
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打电话干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟对方商量能不能带我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是南极观测队员的女儿 也是高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还非常了解南极
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你自己打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个 我觉得我不太合适 我怕生而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好像渐渐理解她的性格了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}同感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我按
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我做不到做不到做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想去南极的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打扰一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这不公平 把难事推给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这话我原封不动地还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:43.47,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是小渊泽报濑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好 我叫做白石结月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:03:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结月？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 这名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}维基上找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}五岁起参演CM等 扮演儿童角色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}关注者3.8万？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:27.95,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}フォローバックが止まらない♪　フォローワー…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:27.95,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回关不停歇 关注者…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去年凭借《回关不停歇》一曲作为歌手出道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太羞耻了 有点想死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快拍一张
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}随便上传到社群是侵犯我的肖像权
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.76,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur3\fs33}我能找张彩纸求个签名和掌印吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你当她是大力士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:39.74,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※相扑馆里，印有大力士掌印的彩纸是热卖纪念品。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话说你为什么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你能替我去南极吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南极 你想去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去哪泄漏的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}BBS？推特？发动态？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.83,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没说出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:04:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前观测队在新宿开联欢会的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也受到邀请了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那时候听说了你们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但为什么要找人替代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}简单来说 我不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是北海道出生的 不喜欢天寒地冻的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:20.07,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fn华康俪粗黑\bord0\b0\fs20\1c&H3F3E40&\pos(684,240)\frz293.5}电视节目企划书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:20.07,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fn华康POP1体W9\bord0\b0\fs40\1c&H3F3E40&\frz293.5\pos(638,222)}女高中生\N去南极
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:20.07,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fn华康俪粗黑\bord0\b0\fs20\1c&H3F3E40&\frx340\fry10\pos(432,358)\frz294.6}青空电视台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果要找高中女生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算不是我也对节目主题没有影响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就说了吧 按我的计划来万无一失！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:43.10,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么乱来 什么荒唐 都你说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.89,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这不在计划内吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这不是很顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好啊南极 能去南极了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等我 企鹅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等我 极光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像很痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:05:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 她是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:05:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是唯一的出口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}凉鞋借穿一下 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:23.49,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn@华康楷书体W5\bord0\1c&H474343&\frz287.8\pos(880,168)\frx354\fry10}新　北海道姑娘企划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:23.49,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn华康楷书体W5\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H474343&\frz11.23\frx342\fry20\pos(778,354)}制\N作\N人\N‧\N经\N纪\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是结月的经纪人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫白石民子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也是她的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是说很多次我不要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.07,0:06:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这可由不得你说 这是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已经说过让给她们去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你以为你一句话就能改吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我收回了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在南极做报导吧 她就不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看她多漂亮 跟个艺人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:06:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报导利落吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…现在…在南极…天气…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:07.01,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 听不清你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 我来报导 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家好 我在南极喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日本的大家看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你哪里上镜了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说得好直
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要你多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好吧 那我只好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:33.82,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\fs30\1c&H395A56&\3c&H70CB8F&\frz321.5\pos(800,164)}嗯…虽然我也想去…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:33.82,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs25\1c&HB7CECF&\pos(562,42)\frz320.3}爱菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:33.82,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs25\1c&H58707C&\frz320.3\pos(524,184)}还不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:33.82,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs25\1c&HB7CECF&\frz320.3\pos(482,222)}悠里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:33.82,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs25\1c&H58707C&\frz320.3\pos(352,296)}下周日呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打 打扰一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突然这么说可能有点怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过 能和我做朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:54.01,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(100,0)\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\1c&H304945&\frx334\fry346\pos(650,174)\frz350.5}抱歉…给我点时间再答复你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟你说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等你升到高二 会给你多留休息时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}连一年都不能忍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别担心 会给你留足备考时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想管什么升学考
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我上高中又不是为了考试！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还以为有奇迹发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是报濑口才好点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那日向你不也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以别再提了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:28.64,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有这么受伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎光临…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说服她？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错 那女生好像就是不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你们能说服她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就通过广播电视台的门路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}推荐你们作为随行人员入团 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是说 只要能让她答应去…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是结月已经不在这里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我听说她周日在东京有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以会在饭店住到周六
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}周五周六 就两天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没时间磨蹭了 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经过10点了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就明早上学前 5点？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 你要去吓醒她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就6点？7点？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你给个时间啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她既然那么不情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定有很不想去的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道不是因为她怕冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她说过是「简单来说」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以肯定有其他难以启齿的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向好成熟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么原因？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这我就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我们就是要先问清楚这点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原因啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}糟了 拜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自我嫌弃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:09:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实我也觉得你说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但最后总是先考虑自己的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能没有为别人着想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在才发现？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开个玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俗话说得好 信念坚定与固执己见只有一线之隔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天不去打工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那要不要一起去吃点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南极啊…去得成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 下次再约吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}305号房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么办 跟…跟踪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟着她没意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}装一下 就装碰巧遇上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 你住在这里啊 要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}读书？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 没上的课我得自己补上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里有自助饮料 还能待到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真勤奋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们想谈南极的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 我这边还没什么进展
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们是这么想没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过在这之前 有点事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你为什么不想去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有那么奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为去了南极就能看到企鹅 还有冰山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说不定还能看到极光…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我妈妈跟你们说了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要你们说服我去 之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:11:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:11:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不打自招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过也确实有事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想知道你为什么不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不想说的话…不勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想你们是不会懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是光现在没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是从来 从来没有过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:36.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\blur8\t(0,300,0\blur0)\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H7F7CA5&\rnd5\t(0,4180,0\fs25)\frz8.181\move(276,216,332,274,0,4154)}恭喜{\1c&HB1BD94&}白石结月小妹妹\N{\1c&H7F7CA5&}上电视啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我从四岁起就做儿童演员了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但因为工作忙 几乎没时间和朋友玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我意识过来 生活已经陷入了恶性循环
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我从来没有和朋友吵过架
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵架的对象总是只有妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:13:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我想上了高中 一定要交几个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}参加社团 打工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放学后和朋友去买东西吃 唱卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:13.71,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs25\1c&H555B5F&\frz332.2\pos(662,144)}悠里与爱菜与结月
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:13.71,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\b0\fs15\1c&H9DA6A8&\frz332.2\pos(656,232)}悠里邀请你加入群组
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 下次我们三个一起去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当然啰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有 能一起拍张照吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结月这么有名 我想给朋友们看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也要 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗 那拜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第一印象是很重要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果现在不努力融入进去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些朋友关系和小圈子 都会固化定型的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突然好想抱紧你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我懂你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也很讨厌新学期开始呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你才不懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为你们都是好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们几个才认识一个月不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也没在一起玩过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是想去同一个地方而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少现在来说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉打扰到这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希望你妈妈能理解你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才要谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟你们聊完 心情也平静点了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以结论到底是怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么结论
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你忘了吗 我们是来说服结月的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 但要是结月拒绝去 报濑就能代替她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说服她的话 就能一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 但要是结月拒绝去 报濑就能代替她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No 思绪一片混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪有那么复杂！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是她拒绝去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定有别的艺人能替代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我们只有说服她这条路可走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我觉得这样子也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:47.86,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3E4638&\frz309.4\pos(266,346)}抱歉…下次有时间再一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:49.48,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H3E4638&\frz309.4\pos(454,428)}抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:49.48,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H3E4638&\pos(380,492)\frz308.3}下次有时间再一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是第一次 有人那样对待我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朋友就是像那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们一起去南极吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们在做什么啊 会被骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别废话了 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}风很大 快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把手伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好怪的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:04.45,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\b0\bord0\fs25\1c&HBFBAA6&\frz340.6\move(516,446,520,284,34,3246)}爱菜退出了群组
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:04.45,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\b0\bord0\fs25\1c&HBCB8A2&\frz340.6\move(440,584,444,418,0,3246)}悠里退出了群组
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:44.00,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そっと记した梦　言い訳ばかりして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:54.75,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ほったらかしにしていた　叶うのが怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:19:03.39,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何があるのかも　何が変わるのかも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:08.92,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}行ってみなきゃ分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:17.07,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあ　一歩前に　踏み出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:23.39,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}大きな梦を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:27.90,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ハルカ　トオクトオク
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:32.47,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真っ白な世界に　残したいな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:37.22,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}最初の足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:42.61,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}大きな梦を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:47.06,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ハルカ　トオクトオク
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:51.80,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真っ白な世界に　残したいな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:56.68,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}最初の足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:20:06.31,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界の最果てで　転がっていく太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:12.09,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}南风はやがて岛を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:16.63,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}髪を揺らす
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:36.42,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}小さな梦を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:41.15,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}愿えた　ツヨクツヨク
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:43.64,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}履き惯れたスニーカー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:50.28,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}纽をギュッと缔め直して
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:55.81,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}でかい梦を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:21:00.26,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ハルカ　トオクトオク
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:04.93,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}波に揺られてかたふりして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:09.93,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}进んでいくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:14.30,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}宇宙より远くへ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:44.00,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}偷偷记下了梦想 却只找了一堆借口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:54.75,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}想到自己总是忘记梦想 就怕去实现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:19:03.39,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}怕出什么事 怕有什么变故
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:08.92,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}但驻足不前 就什么都明白不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:17.07,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向前一步 迈出勇敢的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:23.39,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想实现心底大大的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:27.90,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向那遥远不可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:32.47,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}想在那一片纯白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:37.22,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}留下我最初的脚印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:42.61,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想实现心底大大的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:47.06,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向那遥远不可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:51.80,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}想在那一片纯白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:56.68,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}留下我最初的脚印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:20:06.31,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}红红的一轮夕阳 沉入了世界的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:12.09,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}海面南风跨越万千岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:16.63,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}吹动起我的发梢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:36.42,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想实现心底小小的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:41.15,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}用力再用力 向神明许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:43.64,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}穿上熟悉的运动鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:50.28,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}紧紧地系好鞋带
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:55.81,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想实现心底大大的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:21:00.26,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向那遥远不可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:04.93,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就在波涛之中举杯高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:09.93,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}继续一步步前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:14.30,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}去比宇宙更遥远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就说太早了吧 人家还穿着睡衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是报濑说要来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没得选择啊 之后还要去东京呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}东京？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 听说结月要去东京工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果方便的话 想跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 来之前没打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁叫这家伙没问联络方式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:18:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的错？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:18:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的吗 那我们就去东京的南极…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的错？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还能是谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但提议一起去的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是说 带上她们三个我就去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不然我可不答应去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 结月 出发啰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.13,0:20:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}企…企鹅！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.15,0:20:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毛茸茸的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毛茸茸 毛茸茸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 这里可以进来耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里好挤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现役的是更新型的雪地车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}微速直线前进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:54.54,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※此处是海军用语。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这可不是船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}双层床只剩上层的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}室内会控制在20度以上 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外面会是零下10度 肯定会冷到流鼻涕的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家再靠近点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真正的极光会更漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈跟我说过 美到让人看了都想哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是极光可不容易见到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.55,0:21:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那如果我们能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能就是世界仅有的 在南极看极光的高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对啊 这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:21:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会有点想死呢！
Comment: 0,0:21:59.99,0:22:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.15,0:22:20.84,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}长いトンネルの出口を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:31.76,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}かすかな光の匂いがしてる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.13,0:22:37.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}间违っても　笑えるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:48.33,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}ここから始めよう　仆は旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.54,0:22:59.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}污れた真ん丸のビー玉　握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.24,0:23:10.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}言えなかった言叶も　きっと见つかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.51,0:23:15.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}バカにされたって构わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.97,0:23:21.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}信じてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.15,0:22:20.84,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}寻找着漫长隧道的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:31.76,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}向着泛着微光气味的方向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.13,0:22:37.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}就算走错了 也别忘了微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:48.33,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}从这里开始 我将踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.54,0:22:59.08,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}紧紧捏住手心里 脏脏的玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.24,0:23:10.35,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}没说出口的话 我也一定会找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.51,0:23:15.97,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}随你们嘲笑吧 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.97,0:23:21.30,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}要相信自己 迈出脚步
